text = "[b]KEYBOARD[/b]
WASD / Arrows: Movement / Drive
E: Interact / Repair / Enter Car
X: Extract (Hold when safe)
Space: Handbrake (Car) / Jump (Foot)
Shift: Sprint
F1: Help

[b]GAMEPAD[/b]
Left Stick: Move / Steer
Right Trigger (R2): Gas
Left Trigger (L2): Brake / Reverse
Square / X: Interact
Circle / B: Extract
Cross / A: Handbrake / Jump
L3: Sprint"

